      <h3>Kent &amp; Curwen Royal Charity Polo Cup</h3>
      <p>
        On July 21st, the Kent &amp; Curwen Royal Charity Polo Cup was
        hosted at Lord Andrew Lloyd Webber’s Berskhire Estate, Watership
        Down. The glamourous event saw over 400 VIP guests attend to support
        Sentebale and Tusk Trust - Prince Harry and Prince William’s
        respective charities.
      </p>
      <p>
        Special Guests included Prince Harry of Wales, Lord and Lady Lloyd
        Webber, Sabrina Fung, Aaron Kwok, Timothy Fok, Lady Gabriella
        Windsor, Lady Henrietta Spencer Churchill, and Twiggy.
      </p>
